For 1NF:
We have multiple phone numbers and patients associated with doctors, so split the table into 3 parts.
Following are the tables achieved with their contents after 1NF
Doctor details (Table 1): Doc No., Name, Address, Department Id, Designation, charges per hour (PK = Doc No.)
