For 2NF:
In table 3, patient name, CNIC, phone are dependent on the primary key partially (only on Patient no., not on doc no.)
So split the table 3 as
Doctor-patient relation (Table 5): Doc No., Patient no., room no., room type, bed no. (PK = Doc No.+ Patient no.)
