For 3NF: 
In table 1, charges per hour depends on designation of the doctor. According to 3NF, there should not be any transitive dependency (i.e. there should not be any non-key ïƒ  non-key dependency)
So split the table 1 as:
DocDetails (Table 7): Doc No., Name, Address, Department Id, Designation (PK = Doc No.)
Doc No.	Doc Name	Address	Department Id	Designation
D1	Dr. Nadeem	Abc 123	Neurology	Professor
