D4	Dr. Erum	Ak123	ENT/Neurology	Asst. Professor
D5	Dr. Hafeez	Nd123	Skin/Orthopedic	Asst. Professor


Charge chart (Table 8): Designation, charges per hour (PK = Designation)
Designation
	Charge per hour
Professor	5000
Asst. Professor	3000



Also in table 5, room type is dependent on room number
So split the table 5 as:
